{"tid":1840832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湖北武漢漢口一名醫生因新型冠狀病毒肺炎離世","createTime":"2020-01-25T04:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T04:32:26.000Z","uid":342308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b167e78f2d317516f0ef259c29fed6917e67e004","tid":1840832,"uid":342308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />醫生都無法救自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&ldquo;1月25日早上9点12分，湖北省中西医结合医院（新华医院）耳鼻喉科门诊一名工作人员告诉澎湃新闻，2020年1月16日，该院耳鼻喉科医生梁武东疑似感染新型冠状病毒肺炎，18日，其转到金银潭医院就诊，于1月25日早上7时许不幸去世，享年62岁。<br />\n来源：澎湃新闻&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_5631292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thepaper.cn%2FnewsDetail_forward_5631292&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZTxjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=78478895\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_5631292</a>"},{"pid":"25bc3a1b88d6937ea7b35c8181e1a826e3e5f3e0","tid":1840832,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:28:15.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"7a26fe21dba213a0f068eea5c5793bd95a5c9b24","tid":1840832,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:31:28.000Z","msg":"Translate it into Traditional Chinese, thx"},{"pid":"d59e94f8f96d54d8968ec13d5835cc2797762317","tid":1840832,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:32:26.000Z","msg":"等睇共產黨白事當紅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}